700957f-a.title: Bronx: Eastchester Road - Wilkinson Avenue
700957f-a.text:
Eastchester Road, south from (No. 1890) about 150 yards south of
Wilkinson Ave., to Morris Park Ave., showing the thoroughfare being re-
paved by the W.P.A.
September 2, 1936.
Works Frogress Administration.
Federal Art Project photo.
